des:
You can use the Kohinoor Indian Restaurant & Lounge located voice application to ask questions about Kohinoor Indian Restaurant & Lounge located, a locally, family-owned and managed restaurant with roots from the Champaign-Urbana area and recipes from Northern India

After the Welcome Message, here are some questions you can ask:

- "What are your business hours?"
- "What's your address?"
- "Tell me more about the business."
- "What services do you offer?"
- "What payments do you accept?"

And more!
